<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1.44px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 43px; line-height: 1.8em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">郭名滦，男，汉族，共青团员，2002年7月生，江西赣州人，2021年9月入学，现任经济管理学院学生会办公室部门主任。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1.44px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 43px; line-height: 1.8em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 21px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">寒假期间，他积极响应校团委号召，报名参与大学生“返家乡”社会实践。回家后主动到所在地村委会报道，在工作人员的带领下，参与了“迎春日，清扫环境卫生”活动、“房屋门前三包”服务活动、“房屋安全隐患摸排”活动等等。深入基层一线与村民交流，解决他们的困难，为他们提供力所能及的帮助。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.44px; caret-color: red; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">他积极认真对待志愿活动，受到了当地村民的一致好评。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1.44px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 43px; line-height: 1.8em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.44px; caret-color: red; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;"><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/2n18Qa8gmEKJmcxaerUhWsQzbrQeLKrqZbSw67IzFeX5yk5ibsz6Cv5DLD3fhm6ybu13SuqWOIbYb6cYrtWtCbA/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1" alt="图片" width="339" height="190" style="width: 339px; height: 190px;"/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 43px; line-height: 1.8em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">作为一名还在就读的大学生，还未掌握充分的社会工作经验，只能在一旁做一些辅助性的工作，在这过程中认真工作、虚心请教，在工作的过程中逐渐掌握了各种工作方法，学习到了在学校书本上学不到了的东西。实践是检验真理的唯一标准，在实践之前我只知道一些理论的字面意思，在亲身经历后才知道其中的深刻含义。在志愿服务的这段时间里，我学到了很多东西。在以后的学习之余我会继续参与志愿服务活动，把自己的所学回馈社会。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-indent: 0em; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: right; line-height: 1.8em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">——B210505郭名滦</span></p><p><br/></p>